 "remarks": "Rare opportunity to own one of just four residences in the desirable Forest Glen Condominium Association, ideally located moments from downtown New Canaan, the train, shops, and the renowned restaurants along Forest Street. Offering 2,326 square feet of living space, this spacious condominium lives much like a single-family home with two bedrooms, three full bathrooms, and a versatile first-floor room that provides the flexibility for a guest room, home office, or first-floor bedroom. Meticulously maintained by its original owner, the home has been thoughtfully refreshed with freshly painted interiors, newly refinished hardwood floors, a new furnace, and new central air conditioning. Generous living and entertaining spaces flow seamlessly to a private terrace and backyard, creating the perfect setting for outdoor dining, gardening, or simply relaxing. The unfinished lower level offers exceptional storage and exciting potential for future expansion. Additional highlights include a one-car garage and low-maintenance condominium living in a boutique four-unit association. A rare combination of space, privacy, updates, and an unbeatable in-town location.",
